00:02:24.950 --> 00:02:26.690
we can't do what
we've been doing

00:02:26.690 --> 00:02:30.560
because current patterns of
food production and consumption

00:02:30.560 --> 00:02:33.410
aren't good for our
bodies or for the planet.

00:02:33.410 --> 00:02:35.750
Earlier this year, the
EAT-Lancet commission

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:38.330
