If you think about sort of
these old models that are not

00:26:22.870 --> 00:26:26.530
so crazy, how do we bring them
into the 21st century using

00:26:26.530 --> 00:26:29.710
the technologies that we have?

00:26:29.710 --> 00:26:32.660
And then the other one is
something really interesting.

